    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >About</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Survive this horror/puzzle adventure. Uncover the secrets of a cursed video game from the '80s while a malevolent entity hunts you. Solve escape room-style puzzles, navigate eerie labyrinths, and see how your actions in the game shape the real world. Stay sharp... and stay alive.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220620/extras/b5442046df54eb38ac0e436b5a10b475.poster.avif?t=1760358568\" width=315 height=315 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220620/extras/b5442046df54eb38ac0e436b5a10b475.webm?t=1760358568\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >In Benny Bash you will...</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Face puzzles in the escape room style. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Uncover a horror story as you progress.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play cursed 80s games.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore eerie environments.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover how your actions in the game shape the real world and vice versa.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220620/extras/05675dde408128ad10fea86162005f55.poster.avif?t=1760358568\" width=600 height=192 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220620/extras/05675dde408128ad10fea86162005f55.webm?t=1760358568\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220620/extras/05675dde408128ad10fea86162005f55.mp4?t=1760358568\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
